- "completed surveys since the dawn of 2022" refers to surveys with a status of 'completed' and readings taken on or after January 1, 2022;
- "more than five completed surveys" refers to the count of survey IDs grouped by equipment name being greater than 5;
- "average, highest, and lowest resistivity readings" refer to the average, maximum, and minimum resistivity values from the survey readings.

